{"tid":2197214,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"推到完場 港台31議事論事","createTime":"2020-09-10T12:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T13:02:12.000Z","uid":54517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"df82e9bd4fcc54eb9b49d61a671b56bca294d3fd","tid":2197214,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:20:52.000Z","msg":"監製：馬占威<br />\n主持：曾鈺成 余若薇 陳月慧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n臨近2020年立法會選舉前兩個月，全國人大常委會決議延後香港第六屆立法會至少一年，民主派陣營隨即就延任問題，陷入分岐。<br />\n去年因政府修訂《逃犯條例》引發的一連串社會事件，疫情期間一度沈寂，在疫情過後，示威、衝突場面會否重現？<br />\n《港區國安法》實施後，西方社會質疑香港「一國兩制」名存實亡，對香港政局又會帶來什麼影響？<br />\n全新一輯《議事論事》，繼續緊貼議會現況及時局焦點，為觀眾剖析時弊。"},{"pid":"a1fe0563a90a0489ba9388564b802a50833add44","tid":2197214,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9095683a062fa02ce9419743bddeb00c03e2f50","tid":2197214,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"好少見老鼠曾有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea0f50b38afa7a3d51e24d0069dc81273269c26","tid":2197214,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"老鼠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f952faad4e73a0658deab09d54984027358c63ae","tid":2197214,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eea0f50b38afa7a3d51e24d0069dc81273269c26","tid":2197214,"ui